creator: HouzQuest
descriptionHtml:
Buying a new home can be an exciting, fun, and sometimes daunting journey. HouzQuest is your go-to guide and is with you every step of the way. By providing up to the minute information at the local level for the neighbourhoods you care about most, HQ helps you find that perfect house to make your home.

But HQ doesn’t stop there. Our vetted and approved vendor referrals will make the entire home buying process seamless from start to finish. From local lenders and real estate professionals who can focus on your specific needs and negotiate the best deal for you, to the contractor around the corner who can help apply the elbow grease needed after you move in to make everything just right, HQ is the resource you need to make your home buying journey a stress-free success.
descriptionShort: Home search application for home buyers with up to the minute local information
